<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢ - بُعْد <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{فَبَصُرَتْ بِهِ عَنْ جُنُبٍ وَهُمْ لاَ يَشْعُرُونَ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
